person: Cohn recomments Kayne for membership in the American Society of Biological Chemists, as well as for Assistant Professor at University of Pennsylvania in 1975, and then for a molecular bioligist in 1977 at Colorado State University, again in 1976 she recommends her to Bryn Mawr (see "Z" folder). Kayne worked with Cohn in her laboratory.
